  "description": "T1 - English oak \nReduce canopy by 20-30% \nThe lower canopy of the tree has been previously reduced and has now grown out of proportion to the the tree and property. \nWe would like to remove the ivy that grows throughout the canopy to encourage more sunlight onto the garden below.",
